---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - Skyabove"
  description="Skyabove's Terms of Service. Terms and conditions governing the use of our website and services."
>
  <Navigation />

  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-header">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: January 18, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            Welcome to Skyabove. These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your
            access to and use of our website, services, and products
            (collectively, the "Services"). By accessing or using our Services,
            you agree to be bound by these Terms.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you do not agree to these Terms, you may not access or use our
            Services. If you are using our Services on behalf of an
            organization, you represent and warrant that you have the authority
            to bind that organization to these Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>2. Description of Services</h2>
          <p>
            Skyabove provides comprehensive marketing, AI development,
            automation, and business growth services, including but not limited
            to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Marketing strategy and campaign management</li>
            <li>AI-powered content creation and optimization</li>
            <li>Website development and design</li>
            <li>Search engine optimization (SEO) and local search</li>
            <li>Social media marketing and management</li>
            <li>Search engine marketing (SEM) and display advertising</li>
            <li>Growth marketing and conversion rate optimization</li>
            <li>AI visibility and emerging technology implementation</li>
            <li>Business automation and AI integration</li>
            <li>Analytics and performance tracking</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any aspect
            of our Services at any time, with or without notice.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>3. Service Plans and Pricing</h2>

          <h3>3.1 Pricing</h3>
          <p>
            Our comprehensive marketing and AI services start at $2,000 per
            month. Pricing may vary based on the scope of services, complexity,
            and specific client needs. All pricing will be outlined in a
            separate service agreement or statement of work.
          </p>

          <h3>3.2 Payment Terms</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Services are billed monthly in advance</li>
            <li>Payment is due upon receipt of invoice</li>
            <li>
              We accept payment via credit card, ACH transfer, or wire transfer
            </li>
            <li>
              Late payments may be subject to a 1.5% monthly interest charge
            </li>
            <li>
              Setup fees or onboarding costs may apply and will be specified in
              your agreement
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3>3.3 Commitment Period</h3>
          <p>
            Our services require a 3-month minimum commitment. After the initial
            3-month period, services continue on a month-to-month basis unless
            otherwise specified in your service agreement.
          </p>

          <h3>3.4 Price Changes</h3>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to adjust pricing with 30 days' written notice.
            Price changes will not affect your current billing cycle.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>4. Cancellation and Refunds</h2>

          <h3>4.1 Cancellation by Client</h3>
          <p>
            You may cancel your services after the 3-month minimum commitment
            period by providing 30 days' written notice. Cancellation during the
            initial 3-month period may result in payment of remaining commitment
            fees.
          </p>

          <h3>4.2 Cancellation by Skyabove</h3>
          <p>We reserve the right to terminate services immediately if you:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Violate these Terms of Service</li>
            <li>Fail to make payment within 15 days of the due date</li>
            <li>Engage in illegal, fraudulent, or abusive behavior</li>
            <li>Provide false or misleading information</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>4.3 Refund Policy</h3>
          <p>
            Services are provided on a month-to-month basis. We do not provide
            refunds for partial months or unused services. All fees paid are
            non-refundable unless otherwise specified in writing.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>5. Client Responsibilities</h2>

          <h3>5.1 Cooperation and Information</h3>
          <p>You agree to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Provide accurate, complete, and timely information necessary to
              perform the services
            </li>
            <li>Grant access to necessary accounts, platforms, and systems</li>
            <li>
              Respond to requests for feedback, approvals, and decisions in a
              timely manner
            </li>
            <li>Assign a primary point of contact for communication</li>
            <li>Provide brand guidelines, assets, and content as needed</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>5.2 Account Access</h3>
          <p>
            You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of any
            account credentials you provide to us. You agree to notify us
            immediately of any unauthorized use of your accounts.
          </p>

          <h3>5.3 Compliance</h3>
          <p>
            You represent and warrant that your business, products, and services
            comply with all applicable laws, regulations, and industry
            standards. You are responsible for ensuring that all content and
            materials you provide do not infringe on third-party rights or
            violate any laws.
          </p>
        </section>

