          <h2>6. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>

          <h3>6.1 Ownership of Deliverables</h3>
          <p>
            Upon full payment for services, you will own the following
            deliverables created specifically for you:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Custom website code and design (excluding third-party components)
            </li>
            <li>Original content created for your campaigns</li>
            <li>
              Custom graphics and visual assets created specifically for your
              brand
            </li>
            <li>Campaign strategies and documentation</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>6.2 Skyabove Property</h3>
          <p>Skyabove retains ownership of:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Proprietary tools, processes, and methodologies</li>
            <li>AI systems and automation frameworks</li>
            <li>Templates, frameworks, and pre-existing materials</li>
            <li>Analytics systems and reporting tools</li>
            <li>
              Know-how and intellectual property developed before or independent
              of your engagement
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3>6.3 Third-Party Accounts and Assets</h3>
          <p>You own and retain full access to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>All social media accounts created or managed on your behalf</li>
            <li>Advertising accounts (Google Ads, Meta Ads, LinkedIn, etc.)</li>
            <li>Domain names and hosting accounts</li>
            <li>Email marketing lists and CRM data</li>
            <li>Analytics accounts and historical data</li>
            <li>Developed audiences and custom segments</li>
          </ul>

