            Unless you specifically request otherwise in writing, Skyabove may
            use your project as a case study and include it in our portfolio,
            marketing materials, and client presentations. We will not disclose
            confidential or sensitive information without your express written
            consent.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>7. Confidentiality</h2>

          <h3>7.1 Confidential Information</h3>
          <p>
            Both parties agree to keep confidential any proprietary or sensitive
            information disclosed during the course of our engagement,
