          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Google Ads, Analytics, and Search Console</li>
            <li>Meta (Facebook/Instagram) Business Suite and Ads</li>
            <li>AI platforms (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, etc.)</li>
            <li>Content creation tools (Midjourney, DALL-E, Canva, etc.)</li>
            <li>Marketing automation platforms</li>
