          <p>
            These Terms begin when you first access our Services or sign a
            service agreement and continue until terminated in accordance with
            these Terms.
          </p>

          <h3>12.2 Effect of Termination</h3>
          <p>Upon termination:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>You must pay all outstanding fees and charges</li>
            <li>We will provide access to deliverables and data you own</li>
            <li>
